stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> START
    START --> LOAD_CONFIG
    LOAD_CONFIG --> CONNECT_RENDEZVOUS
    CONNECT_RENDEZVOUS --> REGISTER_IDENTITY
    REGISTER_IDENTITY --> PROBE_TCP_MAPPING

    PROBE_TCP_MAPPING --> WAIT_FOR_PAIR: candidate stable
    PROBE_TCP_MAPPING --> PROBE_RETRY: probe failed
    PROBE_RETRY --> PROBE_TCP_MAPPING
    PROBE_RETRY --> FAILED: retry budget exhausted

    WAIT_FOR_PAIR --> RECEIVE_SESSION
    RECEIVE_SESSION --> SELECT_ROLE
    SELECT_ROLE --> WAIT_FOR_START_TIME

    WAIT_FOR_START_TIME --> PUNCH_CONNECT
    PUNCH_CONNECT --> PUNCH_CONNECTED: SO_ERROR == 0
    PUNCH_CONNECT --> PUNCH_WAVE_RETRY: timeout, RST, or EINPROGRESS expired
    PUNCH_WAVE_RETRY --> PUNCH_CONNECT: next scheduled wave
    PUNCH_WAVE_RETRY --> REPORT_FAILURE: no waves remain

    PUNCH_CONNECTED --> VERIFY_ENDPOINT
    VERIFY_ENDPOINT --> IMPORT_TO_CORE: endpoint valid
    VERIFY_ENDPOINT --> REPORT_FAILURE: endpoint mismatch

    IMPORT_TO_CORE --> CORE_IMPORT_RESPONDER: role = responder
    IMPORT_TO_CORE --> CORE_IMPORT_INITIATOR: role = initiator

    CORE_IMPORT_RESPONDER --> CORE_OWNS_SOCKET: Core creates inbound CNode
    CORE_IMPORT_INITIATOR --> CORE_OWNS_SOCKET: Core creates manual CNode

    CORE_OWNS_SOCKET --> REPORT_SUCCESS
    REPORT_SUCCESS --> MONITOR_PEER
    MONITOR_PEER --> WAIT_FOR_PAIR: disconnected and retry allowed
    MONITOR_PEER --> [*]: stopped

    REPORT_FAILURE --> WAIT_FOR_PAIR: retry allowed
    REPORT_FAILURE --> FAILED: retry budget exhausted
    FAILED --> [*]
